to activate a virtual environment follow these steps
# Windows
 > python-m venv .venv
 > Set-ExecutionPolicy-ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned-Scope CurrentUser
 # macOS
 % python3-m venv .venv

 to activate the virtual environment use:
 > .venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1

 to deactivate, use:
 > deactivate


To provide examples of how to use these query parameters in API requests, such as:
 ### API Query Examples
- **Filter by Title**: `/api/books/?title=The Great Gatsby`
- **Search by Author**: `/api/books/?search=Fitzgerald`
- **Order by Publication Year**: `/api/books/?ordering=-publication_year`
